race.description: Browns Well Tavern, Schlein's Quarries C,G&E Mdn Plate
race.comment: LITTLE ROCKET (2) resumes from a long break. Has shown ability and returns here on the back of a trial and with the blinkers on. Will be winding up late. THAVMA (9) is fitter for two runs in and looks close to a win after a solid fourth at the provincials last time. Drawn to feature. MELODIA LEGEND (5) is worth watching the betting closely. Placed last time at Goulburn for the Freedmans and has since changed yards. One of the few with upside and can kick off with a big run. CANGRANDE (12) is another big watch. First starter for the Jolly yard and is well educated with a strong of trials. Blinkers on and worth watching for a positive push.
